# LucidGate example list: bannedheaderlist
# Format: One lowercase or mixed-case header phrase per line, normally "Header-Name: value-fragment".
# Lines beginning with # are comments and are ignored by the loader.
# To activate a rule, copy one example, remove the leading # and adapt it to your environment.
# You can include another file with: .Include<relative-or-absolute-path>
#
# Commented examples:
# x-tracker: enabled
# x-risk-score: high
# x-debug-mode: true
# user-agent: blocked-client
# referer: http://untrusted.example
# authorization: bearer test-token
# x-forwarded-for: 10.0.0.1
# x-leak-marker: secret
# cookie: tracking_id=
# x-experiment: unsafe
